<task id="integrating-webhelp-plugin-with-dita-ot">
  <title>Installing WebHelp Responsive </title>
  <titlealts>
    <navtitle>Installing</navtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p id="p_gxv_dgk_54b">The requirements of the <ph keyref="product"/> for the <abbreviated-form
          keyref="glossentry-dita-ot"/> are as follows:<ul id="ul_jcr_211_gs">
          <li id="li_hxv_dgk_54b" irina="irina">Java 17 or later.</li>
          <li id="li_ixv_dgk_54b" irina="irina"><abbreviated-form keyref="glossentry-dita-ot"/>
            <ph keyref="DITAOTVersion"/> (includes Saxon 10.x libraries).<note id="note_jxv_dgk_54b"
              >The <ph keyref="product"/> has only been tested with this specific version:
                (<b>DITA-OT <ph keyref="DITAOTVersion"/></b>. It is possible for the plugin to work
              with other versions, but only this version is fully supported.</note></li>
        </ul></p>
      <p id="p_kxv_dgk_54b">To install and integrate the <ph keyref="product"/> with the <abbreviated-form
          keyref="glossentry-dita-ot"/>, follow these steps:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Download and install <xref
            href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html" format="html"
            scope="external">Java 17 or later</xref>.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Download and unpack the <xref href="http://www.dita-ot.org/download" format="html"
            scope="external">DITA Open Toolkit</xref> version <ph keyref="DITAOTVersion"
          />.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd><ph conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-chapter/step_donwload"/></cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd><ph conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-chapter/step_copy_content"/></cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd><xref href="register-webhelp-plugin.dita#register-webhelp-plugin">Register your license
            key</xref>.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd><ph conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-chapter/step_run_integrator"/></cmd>
        <info>
          <ul conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-chapter/script-ul" id="ul_lxv_dgk_54b">
            <li id="li_mxv_dgk_54b" irina="irina"/>
          </ul>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>To test the installation, initiate a publishing process by using one of the options
          found here: <xref href="whr_generate_output.dita"/>.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
